{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"875599a7c0","title":"中央首长对中国京剧院演员的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"013d17838c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":7,"articleId":"875599a7c0"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"},{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"967b946b38","type":"title","text":"中央首长对中国京剧院演员的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"0b268c4021","type":"authors","text":"江青周恩来陈伯达","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"e1add31ca6","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年八月七日晚，周总理、陈伯达、康生、江青等中央首长观看了中国京剧院演出的《智取威虎山》并接见部分演员及音乐工作人员，进行了亲切的谈话，做了重要指示。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"50555d6960","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理：（问王晶华）你的嗓子完全恢复了？","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"d35040a8a7","type":"paragraph","text":"王晶华：完全恢复了。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"cd325cc375","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（问王世荣、陈文珍）你们是做什么的？","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"1494bf2225","type":"paragraph","text":"王、陈：拉胡琴。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"16fb862753","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们的胡琴拉的不错么。前半场也是你们拉的吗？","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"aba7a49545","type":"paragraph","text":"王、陈：不是，是另外两个同志拉的。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"303d7b0da6","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们的胡琴拉的都不错么，很好。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"74c4aa52e9","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：冯志孝现在也不错么，过去一唱就摇头，现在也能挺起来了。（对李长春）你头一场可能是理解的不对，妻子被打死了，喊“孩子他妈”应该望着她，现在你的眼睛望着别的地方，这样不合理。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"a2401c0786","type":"paragraph","text":"另外一个地方，这恐怕是普遍的毛病。几个剧团演的时候都有这个毛病，就是敌人把孩子扔到深渊里摔死，应该往下看，看深渊。常宝那一段唱应设计成英姿挺拔，因为她在深山生活象个男孩子，现在婉约太多，应请于会咏同志再搞一下（姚文元同志说，已经告诉上海了）。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"7984d07b32","type":"paragraph","text":"（对谢锐青）你的化妆是不是有些问题？你多大了！","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"c86ca5fd65","type":"paragraph","text":"谢锐青：三十四了。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"093e478d14","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：（对钱浩梁）“深山问苦”这一场你没有进入角色。当猎户老常说出山后有一条险路直通威虎山的时候，你找到了一条路，应该是非常惊喜，有明显的表情。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"627be18203","type":"paragraph","text":"第八场，杨子荣说“又是试探”应该念的非常清楚。（江青同志示范）。座山雕走后，杨子荣说：“这个笨蛋。”是暗语说的，内心独白，声音不要高，你现在声音这样高，座山雕刚走不远，不就让他听见了！这些地方还应该好好琢磨琢磨。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"ccb75a469a","type":"paragraph","text":"（对冯志孝）少剑波接到杨子荣的情报后说：“老杨，英雄。”应该是从内心里发出来的，念得非常亲切，杨子荣是自己多年的战友，应该感到非常自豪。（江青同志示范）靠集体的力量再磨一磨。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"e744ea6700","type":"paragraph","text":"（对景荣庆）座山雕应该再凶狠、残暴一些。不要太草包了。你是唱架子花脸的吧？","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"a109639b65","type":"paragraph","text":"景荣庆：是。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"eae93ff2db","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：你的嗓子还不错么，你能跃起来吗？","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"ac66501b9f","type":"paragraph","text":"景荣庆：能。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"fbf5def9c6","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：杨子荣劈下去一刀，你应该跳起来。座山雕是很狡猾的，他没有本事就不能当三朝元老。这个戏公演几场了！","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"0cad7043e1","type":"paragraph","text":"答：×场。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"0e4fb006e3","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：剧场里有没有冷气？","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"25feff8b5b","type":"paragraph","text":"众答：前边有，后台没有，可以送冷风。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"bbffba473e","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：演得不错，很整齐。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"806b7a20f6","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：演得不错。","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"6bb204390c","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：再熟悉熟悉。冯志孝要练武功。你多大了！","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"54424e088c","type":"paragraph","text":"冯志孝：二十八了。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"d2f6c0ffc3","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：（对钱浩梁）你多大了！","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"9dfc7d775e","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：三十二了。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"13fd26d0f0","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（问王晶华）你多大了。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"f94863cac5","type":"paragraph","text":"王晶华：二十八了。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"28ef9869ab","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：你们这个团大多数都是三十岁左右吧？","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"8521ffc7f5","type":"paragraph","text":"众答：平均不到三十岁。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"8756fe1111","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：文的要练武，武的要练唱。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"7b37c94bac","type":"paragraph","text":"（对李长春）你也应该练武功，还小呢，方三十岁么。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"7160f91b94","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：冯志孝嗓子不错么。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"7c82bce87e","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：（问李长春）你演《海港》了吗？","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"4f920e599d","type":"paragraph","text":"李长春：没有。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"048152332e","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：我们看了一场你演的《海港》很长气。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"06befa9f48","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（问张长海）你叫什么名字？","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"735d028967","type":"paragraph","text":"张长海：张长海。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"da59071a01","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：演什么的？","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"98dab44dcc","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：演孙达得，过去也是演长靠武生。","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"5464c5e86b","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：看样子象个演武生的。","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"3ed726f78c","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：你有嗓子吗？","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"c9387eb166","type":"paragraph","text":"张长海：没有。嗓子不行。","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"56d347a199","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：没有可以练。有嗓子的都要练唱。（问马永贵）你有嗓子吗？","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"34978c15a1","type":"paragraph","text":"别人答：他有嗓子。","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"},{"id":"35f257b586","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：有嗓子的都要练嗓子，文的要练武，武的要练唱，能文能武，对革命现代戏来说，老的不是多了而是不够了。要创出一条新的路子来。你们很累了，早点休息吧！","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0"}],"page":{"id":"947119313c","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"875599a7c0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}